|N@e 'l dir... facea~: The first "dir" is the
subject of "facea," and "andar" is the object; then "andar"
becomes the subject and "lui" (i.e., |dir~) the object.
..TEXT:
|andavam forte... vento~: Cf. ^Purg.~ IV, 88-93.
..TEXT:
|forte~: "Rapidly."  Cf. ^Purg.~ XI, 19.
