..TEXT:
|ammirazione traean~ = ^traevano ammirazione.~
^Trarre~ can mean either "to draw" or "to shoot."  The latter
meaning seems to fit the context better, the object being
"ammirazione... di me."  For ^trarre~ in this sense, cf. ^Purg.~
III, 69.
